---
title: Balsamic Roasted Tomatoes with Feta, Pearl Barley and Za'atar Veggies
description: So often, the way we cook ingredients is just as important as which ingredients we choose. Take these simple roma tomatoes. When roasted, then drizzled with sweet balsamic dressing, their flavour is really elevated to new heights!
